        {
            "title": "羅湖口岸｜衫袋藏含大麻電子煙 男客過關閃閃縮縮斷正",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/f9659910fca71a2ce7f9e3a8c8521f1e/2025-04/Clipboard13_4.png\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/3091e3ab168371f0bffc4177d0d10102/fe609ae35b9e4134a7d72794e9804fa6-1276e22b9462904bdcb8b7093c4ceb34-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67f88bdf0b548\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67f88bdf0b54a\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"羅湖海關一名男旅客攜帶含大麻煙油的電子煙入境內地時被海關檢獲。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7243e48c223caeaa6d31d9e3f0ac5ac5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250411/_2025041111240284898.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">羅湖海關一名男旅客攜帶含大麻煙油的電子煙入境內地時被海關檢獲。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>近日，羅湖海關一名男旅客攜帶含大麻煙油的電子煙入境內地時被海關檢獲。\n\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/u/5832321505\">海關發布</a>稱，關員在對進境旅客進行監管時，發現一名旅客進入海關監管區未向海關申報，且試圖躲避海關檢查。海關關員隨即對其進行攔截。經進一步檢查，在當事人左側上衣口袋內發現裝有煙油的電子煙一支，淨重16.8克。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3445215/\">中港車皇崗口岸出境 偷運3條瀕危金龍魚被截</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"男子攜含大麻電子煙過關閃閃縮縮。 海關發布\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fc1d87abcaa5d4bd162b2e6aa63de613/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-11-11h11m25s378.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子攜含大麻電子煙過關閃閃縮縮。 海關發布\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"男子被截查。 海關發布\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8f652a52fed14bd5c19b765f1f8b2f87/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-11-11h11m32s254.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子被截查。 海關發布\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"男子被搜查。 海關發布\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e91891d67d37da5e3b0df7734da91875/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-11-11h11m37s932.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子被搜查。 海關發布\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"男子衫袋中的電子煙。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3bc588e27657e6e3b468e66e09f1c585/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-11-11h11m47s299.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子衫袋中的電子煙。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"電子煙油呈大麻陽性反應。 海關發布\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6b0b716edc7ca04b4df7dd8bfc0c7738/2025-04/Clipboard12_0_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        電子煙油呈大麻陽性反應。 海關發布\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>經快速檢測，該電子煙油呈大麻陽性反應。目前，海關已對當事人作立案處理。\n\n</p>\n<p>大麻在內地屬於管制麻醉藥品。走私、運輸毒品，無論數量多少，都會被追究刑事責任，面臨刑事處罰。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
